sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as WorktreeUnlink
    participant WS as WorktreeService
    participant Caddy

    User->>CLI: orbit worktree unlink site worktree
    CLI->>CLI: Parse site and worktree arguments
    
    CLI->>WS: unlinkWorktree siteName worktreeName
    WS->>WS: Find worktree entry
    
    alt Worktree not found
        WS-->>CLI: false
        CLI-->>User: Error - Worktree not found for site
    else Worktree found
        WS->>Caddy: Remove subdomain route
        WS->>Caddy: Reload configuration
        WS-->>CLI: true
        CLI-->>User: Worktree unlinked from site
        CLI-->>User: Caddy configuration updated
    end
